    "download_target_name is the local filename to save in src/rag_docs/",
    "for bank-level analysis, prioritize standalone quarterly, semiannual, and audited financial statements before annual reports",
    "for Vietstock or PHS disclosure pages, download the attached PDF and save it using the filename field below",
    "for files hosted on VBPL page views rather than direct PDFs, open the page and click the PDF download link manually if the script cannot fetch it directly",
